Sample images used by the CLI examples and integration tests.

Everything in this directory must be either synthetic (procedurally
generated with no likeness) or explicitly public-domain. Face
photographs of real people belong in your own local scratch directory,
not the repository — see the .gitignore for the *.protected.* pattern.

Files:

    synthetic_face.png   Procedurally generated ellipse-with-eyes used
                         as a smoke-test target. Not a real face.
